    "Contemporary research in supply chain management emphasizes resilience, risk mitigation, and sustainabilitythese AI tools assist by simulating disruptions, providing predictive insights, and optimizing operations with an environmental focus.",
    "Ethical considerations and bias mitigation remain paramount when utilizing AI tools such as Gemini and ChatGPT.",
    "Both models operate on extensive training datasets, potentially containing inherent biases.",
    "However, they can aid research initiatives aimed at mitigating bias by identifying biases within historical data and current decision-making processes.",
    "Additionally, they highlight ethical concerns that businesses must address for transparent and equitable operations."
